be.ehb.medicationreminder.core

Class MedicationList

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.ehb.medicationreminder.core.MedicationList

  • public class MedicationList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class keeps a list of all the medications that are set to be notified. It is implemented as a singleton, so only one instance can be called.
